keyFacts: An email was sent on March 3, 2021, from 'aMMIla' to an FBI contact in New York.
The email subject references a 'Lake house' and the body states the sender was at a landing and heard a conversation.
The email included attached image files named IMG_2635.jpg and IMG_2639.jpg.
